  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to your first shift at The Ice Bin, a local ice cream parlor, owned by the mysterious Mr. Coil. You have 11 days to generate enough revenue to secure your employment and satisfy your boss. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3613450/extras/124e1a99bcb3da2082b206ae2b1ec0a5.poster.avif?t=1744400424\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3613450/extras/124e1a99bcb3da2082b206ae2b1ec0a5.webm?t=1744400424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3613450/extras/124e1a99bcb3da2082b206ae2b1ec0a5.mp4?t=1744400424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Complete Orders</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete customer orders in timely manner. If you can complete an order in the allocated time, you will be given a tip. Tips are vital for successfully completing a run.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3613450/extras/36f16007d28dded872b3c46a67a201f1.poster.avif?t=1744400424\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3613450/extras/36f16007d28dded872b3c46a67a201f1.webm?t=1744400424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3613450/extras/36f16007d28dded872b3c46a67a201f1.mp4?t=1744400424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Get Upgrades</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After each day, you are given a choice between 3 randomized items that can be used to increase business revenue. Choose your items wisely. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3613450/extras/114cbc63c4757aef76081696e9883569.poster.avif?t=1744400424\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3613450/extras/114cbc63c4757aef76081696e9883569.webm?t=1744400424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3613450/extras/114cbc63c4757aef76081696e9883569.mp4?t=1744400424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Replay</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Refine your skills and test your luck by playing multiple runs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After receiving your daily item, the game will auto-save.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to your first shift at The Ice Bin, a local ice cream parlor, owned by the mysterious Mr. Coil. You have 11 days to generate enough revenue to secure your employment and satisfy your boss. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3613450/extras/124e1a99bcb3da2082b206ae2b1ec0a5.poster.avif?t=1744400424\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3613450/extras/124e1a99bcb3da2082b206ae2b1ec0a5.webm?t=1744400424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3613450/extras/124e1a99bcb3da2082b206ae2b1ec0a5.mp4?t=1744400424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Complete Orders</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete customer orders in timely manner. If you can complete an order in the allocated time, you will be given a tip. Tips are vital for successfully completing a run.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3613450/extras/36f16007d28dded872b3c46a67a201f1.poster.avif?t=1744400424\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3613450/extras/36f16007d28dded872b3c46a67a201f1.webm?t=1744400424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3613450/extras/36f16007d28dded872b3c46a67a201f1.mp4?t=1744400424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Get Upgrades</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After each day, you are given a choice between 3 randomized items that can be used to increase business revenue. Choose your items wisely. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3613450/extras/114cbc63c4757aef76081696e9883569.poster.avif?t=1744400424\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3613450/extras/114cbc63c4757aef76081696e9883569.webm?t=1744400424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3613450/extras/114cbc63c4757aef76081696e9883569.mp4?t=1744400424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Replay</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Refine your skills and test your luck by playing multiple runs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After receiving your daily item, the game will auto-save.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
